      <title>隆巴德利在关键时刻重返英格兰银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/bank-of-england-s-next-rate-decision-may-hang-on-new-deputy-governor-lombardelli</link>
      <description><![CDATA[21 年前，克莱尔·隆巴德利离开英格兰银行，以初级宏观经济学家的身份进入英国财政部工作。周一，她以货币政策副行长的身份重返央行，仅次于行长安德鲁·贝利，此时正值最关键的时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/bank-of-england-s-next-rate-decision-may-hang-on-new-deputy-governor-lombardelli</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国公投后欧元上涨，中国股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/euro-gains-on-french-voting-china-eyed-after-pmi-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元跟随欧洲股指期货上涨，因为市场猜测玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼政党将难以在法国大选中赢得绝对多数席位，这缓解了投资者对欧洲第二大经济体将采取更为激进的政策转变的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/euro-gains-on-french-voting-china-eyed-after-pmi-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 22:48:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市上涨，因押注勒庞无法赢得绝对多数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/euro-ticks-up-with-le-pen-s-party-set-to-win-first-french-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们消化了有关玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼政党有望赢得法国立法议会选举首轮选举的迹象，但其优势比一些民意调查显示的要小，欧元因此走强，欧洲股指期货上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/euro-ticks-up-with-le-pen-s-party-set-to-win-first-french-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 19:40:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
